file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Fruits
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: getRoot
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet1'
        '400':
          description: 'Invalid value for: body'
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
components:
  schemas:
    Pet:
      required:
        - name
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
    Pet1:
      required:
        - legsCount
      type: object
      properties:
        legsCount:
          type: integer
          format: int32
